==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Kibosh
<hw>Ki"bosh</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Nonsense;
stuff; also, fashion; style.</def> <mark>[Slang]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Portland cement when thrown or blown into the
recesses of carved stonework to intensify the shadows.</def></p>

<p><cs><col><b>To put the kibosh on</b></col>, <cd>to dispose of; to
squelch; to terminate; put an end to; to do for.</cd>
<mark>[Slang]</mark></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Kiby</ent>⟦br⟧
